channel.title: Customs won't go into my client
channel.description: Ok ive added countless customs into my client before, but ever since I have changed the name of the client it won't work. I used to be able to put the ints in the class8.java and put the models in the model folder, then compile and run and they would work...Now it won't. Will someone help?
